text: Nabii Mucammadow ġzsateiço Cus: Nabii Ibraahim kee kay Baxi Nabii Ismaaqil kaqbak xexxaar Qideeniih xisne teetik fayya heen waqdi, ken Nammay Yalla kallacak:Ni-Rabbow ta- abnah nan xisnee kee dooqa nek oggolaay nek Raabit, Diggah atu ni-Rabbow Ni-Xaaqo taabbeeh ni-niyat tanim taaxigehik iyyen
